{"tid":1038668,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"在中國的美國老闆們 近1/4延後投資 1/5考慮外移","createTime":"2019-02-26T23:54:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T02:31:34.000Z","uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"24327d54b282225f4edc7ad79d7cb96da1c89e14","tid":1038668,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T23:54:09.000Z","msg":"在中國的美國老闆們 近1/4延後投資 1/5考慮外移<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/6150159/article-%e5%9c%a8%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e7%9a%84%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e8%80%81%e9%97%86%e5%80%91-%e8%bf%911-4%e5%bb%b6%e5%be%8c%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87-1-5%e8%80%83%e6%85%ae%e5%a4%96%e7%a7%bb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F6150159%2Farticle-%25e5%259c%25a8%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e7%259a%2584%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%259c%258b%25e8%2580%2581%25e9%2597%2586%25e5%2580%2591-%25e8%25bf%25911-4%25e5%25bb%25b6%25e5%25be%258c%25e6%258a%2595%25e8%25b3%2587-1-5%25e8%2580%2583%25e6%2585%25ae%25e5%25a4%2596%25e7%25a7%25bb%2F&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6f4N63GW6AE6v5vQ0jPanwo%3D&h=3a0a66af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/6150159/article-%e5%9c%a8%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e7%9a%84%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e8%80%81%e9%97%86%e5%80%91-%e8%bf%911-4%e5%bb%b6%e5%be%8c%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87-1-5%e8%80%83%e6%85%ae%e5%a4%96%e7%a7%bb/</a><br />\n<br />\n今天公布的業界調查顯示，在中國的美國企業看淡未來一年的前景，許多人擔心美中貿易關係惡化，近1/4延後投資。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國商會（American Chamber of Commerce）訪調在中國的314家美企，讓人一窺北京和美國對逾3000億美元商品互徵報復性關稅帶來的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普兩天前表示，他和北京都認為貿易談判有「顯著進展」，因此將延後原定本週對中國商品調高關稅的措施。<br />\n<br />\n美國商會這項調查發現，8成9企業對全球最重要的雙邊關係看法悲觀。<br />\n<br />\n調查指出，關稅直接衝擊美企、增加成本並減少了來自中國消費者的需求，一些企業甚至被迫資遣員工。<br />\n<br />\n美中貿易摩擦是業界最大關切之一，3/4預期今年兩國貿易關係會更惡化或維持不變。<br />\n<br />\n近2/3受訪企業表示，美中貿易緊張影響他們對中國市場的計畫，也有近1/4企業因此延後在中國投資。<br />\n<br />\n根據這份調查，約1/5企業已經或正在考慮把生產線移出中國，關稅和成本高漲是最大原因。"},{"pid":"44a71a9612b02d17812cb43640c017094e43ccde","tid":1038668,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T00:01:59.000Z","msg":"而佢地要離左境先敢講真話"},{"pid":"d4bfb01ac4faa32d9556f1c63865cf3ab6e8a564","tid":1038668,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T00:17:03.000Z","msg":"首先要諗計搬走啲錢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多根本想走走唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ce2032f66f63a14321549620ed9c85b5e27581","tid":1038668,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T00:17:41.000Z","msg":"支那狗拉唒佢地啦，直情要抄家<br />\n話比人知支那係唔驚美帝既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7daeb753298d6063fd05008980685c74d406028e","tid":1038668,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T01:46:48.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a10dd13f5a55faaf32af5fc42a679e33b630a6","tid":1038668,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T02:31:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}